title: Gregg Ranch Formation
text: The Gregg Ranch Formation is a <a href="Formation%20%28geology%29">geologic formation</a> in <a href="California">California</a>. It preserves <a href="fossils">fossils</a> dating back to the <a href="Ordovician">Ordovician</a> <a href="Period%20%28geology%29">period</a>.
